data.description:
24 hour recorded info on this property...1-888-210-3348 X.2628

Gorgeous brick ranch home on 9.16 wooded acres in fabulous Edisto Island waterfront community. This home has been immaculately cared for by the owners and features: eat-in kitchen with abundance of counter and cabinet space; family room with wood burning fireplace; master suite with his & her closets and tub/shower combo; screened porch and deck overlooking the beautiful secluded 9+ acres where you can feed the deer right from your hands!! Also on the property is a 24' x 26' workshop with 240 power, garage door and wood stove...a 10' x 12' storage building, a 20' x 24' concrete pad perfect for boat or RV storage. The neighborhood is amazing boasting a deep water private community dock with 2 large floaters and a deep water ramp for launching your boat. The community is ideally located less than 10 minutes to Edisto Beach and 45 minutes to Downtown Charleston. Also, The well has a precipitating iron filter to remove sulfur.
data.whatILove: Our one story, brick, aluminum and vinyl trim home is very easy to maintain, minimal painting. We have plenty of storage space and closets. Our home sets back from the road so it is quite and secluded but not remote.
